Do you have any hope that the legendary items will help?<br />
 <br />
Personally, I think Lotro is intended to be more about the story than about the itemization.  It shows in their free content releases.  Those all add an epic story book, the same story that has been progressing since release and one that will eventually get to Mordor.  Its the first time I recall a game really getting an epic story in a game that is both singularly focused and really open ended.<br />
 <br />
Its not WoW, not Vanguard, its Lotro.  If you approach the game desiring to be a min-maxer type, its going to be an ultimately disappointing experience.  I don't see that changing.</div>
